.row.jumbotron.returning-header
  .col-md-12
    h1 Welcome Back!
.row
  .col-md-12
    h3 Returning Volunteers
    p
      | Having previously volunteered, your personal data is on file. At the end of this
      |  message you will be asked to sign in to your account to review and update your information for 2016.
    h3 Tournament Package
    p
      | There is again a $35.00 fee to volunteer for the 2016 Tournament. For your
      |  investment you will receive a Self Regional Healthcare Foundation Womenâ€™s Health Classic shirt and hat,
      |  complimentary food and beverage during your shift, parking, and a one-day tournament pass.
    h3 Payment
    p
      | Your $35.00 check should be made payable to The Links at Stoney Point Ladies Golf Classic. You
      |  may leave your payment at the Pro Shop or you may mail it to the address shown on the application.
    h3 Terms and Conditions
    p
